excellent sound, Thank you nappo for placing this torrent and thanks for seeding this :-)

There is a big problem with this torrent. There's many , many skips on the last few songs. I thought maybe the tracking messed up, so I downloaded it again. Same thing! Beware! Too bad because the music is just fabulous. Maybe someone could do this one over.

Sadly it's unplayable towards the end. A real shame; since it's a great performance and, (apart from the glitches), a superb recording. Does anyone know where it's from? Does anyone have a decent version of it? Thanks.
